  "detailed_description": "A cute alpaca arrived at a mysterious place called Wowo Island with great anticipation. On this dreamlike island, it is about to embark on a leisurely and joyful adventure full of surprises. On the island, there are not only beautiful scenery, but also emerald green grasslands under the azure sky, colorful flowers competing with each other, and clear streams flowing gently. There are also numerous magical weapons, such as swords emitting mysterious light and staffs possessing powerful magic. There are even more ferocious monsters, bared their teeth and claws, roaring loudly. But the brave alpaca was fearless, with a steadfast light shining in its eyes. Excitedly, it embarked on this unknown adventure, ready to face all challenges, explore the secrets deep in the island, and write its own legendary story.<br>There are dungeons, mazes, bosses, secret locations, and more in the game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/a2088b01a5f70e823da21c16f1472462.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=350 /></span><br>This is an open world game where you can freely play, upgrade, adventure, decrypt, and discover many secret places. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/7faadc8fb5054f41860a70e4af916159.avif?t=1724138765\" width=400 height=533 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/f519b59167f4bb5da5b8859782360c3c.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=374 /></span><br>Game weapons and equipment effects, right-click will have skill effects. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/9fd2a2cc6e60c39a235be3b9091a9508.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/fc5eaf77b23b6ecfaf1c3827f98251fc.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=360 /></span>、<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/86678630a944bee73dbacb596471a258.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=328 /></span><br>Weapons are located in different parts of the world and require exploration, but they all have level limitations, so you need to upgrade to obtain them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/cf91886a6b6eb05252bf971250295b86.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=312 /></span><br>Take a break and enjoy the scenery while listening to the sea breeze<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/2657fd134ee51bb560c6be61e1ce6c8d.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=300 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A cute alpaca arrived at a mysterious place called Wowo Island with great anticipation. On this dreamlike island, it is about to embark on a leisurely and joyful adventure full of surprises. On the island, there are not only beautiful scenery, but also emerald green grasslands under the azure sky, colorful flowers competing with each other, and clear streams flowing gently. There are also numerous magical weapons, such as swords emitting mysterious light and staffs possessing powerful magic. There are even more ferocious monsters, bared their teeth and claws, roaring loudly. But the brave alpaca was fearless, with a steadfast light shining in its eyes. Excitedly, it embarked on this unknown adventure, ready to face all challenges, explore the secrets deep in the island, and write its own legendary story.<br>There are dungeons, mazes, bosses, secret locations, and more in the game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/a2088b01a5f70e823da21c16f1472462.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=350 /></span><br>This is an open world game where you can freely play, upgrade, adventure, decrypt, and discover many secret places. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/7faadc8fb5054f41860a70e4af916159.avif?t=1724138765\" width=400 height=533 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/f519b59167f4bb5da5b8859782360c3c.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=374 /></span><br>Game weapons and equipment effects, right-click will have skill effects. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/9fd2a2cc6e60c39a235be3b9091a9508.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/fc5eaf77b23b6ecfaf1c3827f98251fc.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=360 /></span>、<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/86678630a944bee73dbacb596471a258.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=328 /></span><br>Weapons are located in different parts of the world and require exploration, but they all have level limitations, so you need to upgrade to obtain them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/cf91886a6b6eb05252bf971250295b86.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=312 /></span><br>Take a break and enjoy the scenery while listening to the sea breeze<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136260/extras/2657fd134ee51bb560c6be61e1ce6c8d.avif?t=1724138765\" width=500 height=300 /></span>",
